precis:
Enactment of the FOREIGN COMPANIES PRESCRIBED TRANSACTIONS REGULATIONS
which provide that reinsurance transactions entered into by a foreign
company in the ordinary course of its business do not require the approval
of the Minister of Finance under subsection 587.1(3) of the Act.
